.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定係已經有證據講trump想暗殺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1af681a90df290a8c7cb821f0ddfc993ce469de","tid":806738,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T04:16:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab9468ae7504f1d00f37d9b11ddf825241ef04a5","tid":806738,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T06:48:41.000Z","msg":"現實: 侵侵撚片天下無敵手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3774cb1b6502db264ed3c3e1ca04d0af792bd8f9","tid":806738,"uid":103922,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T09:13:02.000Z","msg":"係一個有聲望的記者，同trump呢個serial liar之間，一個正常人點都會信個記者而唔係trump。trump你當佢係美國版689就得。"},{"pid":"34a1e06279b1d50b8cab9cf9955f941a1cbd5f21","tid":806738,"uid":65128,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T09:17:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"496d8ee7d7776d7327e62c596e0be417cce11337","tid":806738,"uid":63846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T09:18:40.000Z","msg":"本土派<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}